Onions are some of the food items that can be added to your daily meals because of the health benefits they add to the body. But there are some groups of people that should stay away from onions. In this article, I will educate you on some health conditions that make you avoid onions.
1. The first medical condition that makes you avoid onions is allergies. There are some people around who will always have some health issues like rashes and itchy bodies or eyes each time they consume onions even if it is in small quantity. So, you are advised to stay away from onions if you have an allergy.
2. Another medical condition which makes you to avoid onions is heartburn. Each time a person suffering from heartburn consumes onions, it triggers the heartburn which makes your heart to have a burning sensation. So, you are advised to consult your doctor on a regular basis and stay away from onions.
3. Another dangerous health condition which also makes you to stay away from onions is gas and bloating. If some people consume onions, they tend to have excess gas in their stomachs and also causes bloating.


